FBIS3-15967 "drsov048_a_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Russian, German Spokesmen Decline Comment LD1003222894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1923 GMT 10 Mar 94 LD1003222894 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow March 10 TASS -- The Russian counterintelligence service press centre refused to comment on Thursday on media reports about the arrest of a German spy in Moscow. Russian Intelligence Service spokesman Aleksandr Mikhailov told ITAR-TASS that these reports need to be checked and verified. A German press and information department official told ITAR-TASS in Bonn that he did not receive any such information and therefore could not confirm or comment on the fact of the arrest of the German intelligence agent in Moscow who was said to have worked for the Bundesnachrichtendienst, Germany's intelligence service.
